      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’ve just completely disappeared. everyone only ever knew the version of me that was successful and perfect, but that person is gone now. i messed up everything so bad that there's nothing left of me. it's like the person i was is already dead, so what's even the point of staying here?",
